description: Try this 15-minute kebab recipe at your next barbecue â€“ it's so easy to whip up. The tender kebabs are served on a bed of tasty fried rice.
name: Honey Soy Kebabs With Speedy Fried Rice Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 250g Woolworths COOK stir fry mix superfood vegetables
450g Woolworths microwave steamed long grain white rice

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat chargrill over medium heat. Cook kebabs, turning occasionally, for 8 minutes or until chicken is lightly charred and cooked through.

Meanwhile, heat oil in a wok or large frying pan over medium-high heat. Stir-fry ginger for 30 seconds or until fragrant. Add vegetables and stir-fry for 2 minutes or until almost tender. Add rice and soy sauce, and stir-fry for 2 minutes or until rice is heated through.
Spoon rice onto a serving platter. Top with kebabs and sprinkle with sesame seeds and onion. Serve.
